        "body": "Basically Alma called the april dip well and positioned herself well by buying that dip. Most of her portfolio is long so she only needs to hedge against downside using spreads or option writing. \n\nSomeone who was not in this chat and joined late or did not buy the April dip either has to enter late with buy the dip or has to wait for the 5% pullback which has been non existent. Missing the april window has been brutal for many.",
